metadata.name: AS-05 : ANZIAK
metadata.description:
"Known as AS-05 : ANZIAK and found on a small planet in the Draco II galaxy, this ancient alien skull has features that exhibit a species with multiple unusual sensory abilities on its face, including heat, ultraviolet, voltage, and echolocation. This skull is dated to be over 1.6 billion years old."

Mixed Media Digital Artpiece By Digivatar
Includes files to use for print
Edition 1/1
